org.jasig.cas.services

Class AbstractAttributeReleasePolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jasig.cas.services.AbstractAttributeReleasePolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, AttributeReleasePolicy
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReturnAllAttributeReleasePolicy, ReturnAllowedAttributeReleasePolicy, ReturnMappedAttributeReleasePolicy

    public abstract class AbstractAttributeReleasePolicy
extends Object
implements AttributeReleasePolicy
    Abstract release policy for attributes, provides common shared settings such as loggers and attribute filter config. Subclasses are to provide the behavior for attribute retrieval.
    Since:
    4.1.0
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed
